About Us
Located in Downtown Lake Mary, Citrus City Craft is home to tons of weekly events, live entertainment, a unique list of signature cocktails, and the areaâs most diverse craft beer selection.
Our taproom provides the perfect atmosphere - with TVs in view of every seat. Or spend some time relaxing on the Bent Station Beer Garden with your furriest friend.
TESTIMONIALS
Great craft beer with a full liquor bar and wonderful staff. Have to have a âBerry ya PiÅasâ bomb! Dog friendly! Stop by and say hi to Jeff, Johnny and the rest of the great staff! Indoor and outdoor, you choose how you enjoy your time!

Customer
This place is an amazing neighborhood spot for craft beer and/or liquor drinks. I tried their Jalapeno-Honey Margarita and I cannot get over how delicious it is ! It's sweet and refreshing with the slightest kick. The staff is always helpful and the place is always clean; an easy 5/5 rating.
Bianca
